"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ottimo</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Does the job</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/javnation/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8c59b0c54bdd35ae7cd75e66c2588a2aae8fb7d1e967ebf5c4f0993dc8742e96?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8c59b0c54bdd35ae7cd75e66c2588a2aae8fb7d1e967ebf5c4f0993dc8742e96?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/javnation/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Javnation</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 13, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I like the control WooCommerce gives users over their store. That i am not locked into some corporations infrastructure with no control over costs. Managing plugins can be a pain, as can all the research to see what works and optimizing your site. But overall, it works very well, is affordable and has been quite reliable.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great support!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexcpaige/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7901b50f65b6939a8cac8561f93012ba48def8f79e7fd4a7c06b6e0629f9c194?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7901b50f65b6939a8cac8561f93012ba48def8f79e7fd4a7c06b6e0629f9c194?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexcpaige/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">alexcpaige</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 12, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>very helpful and fast response.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Terrible Customer Service</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lbworks/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c36e0e85f47596ecef7f54eef15b16863427624ffe86e6c3c27901722f983a0f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c36e0e85f47596ecef7f54eef15b16863427624ffe86e6c3c27901722f983a0f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lbworks/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lbworks</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 10, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Avoid WooCommerce like the plague. Absolutely disgusted with WooCommerce and their service is below any standard of acceptance. I am ashamed we are using WooCommerce and will have to rethink our entire platform strategy. WooCommerce is trash. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zougou/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ac92f5f6c259eabef9941f919ed5f5c9b6a166f4059f38aa9e87a7580cefb669?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ac92f5f6c259eabef9941f919ed5f5c9b6a166f4059f38aa9e87a7580cefb669?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zougou/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Zougou</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 10, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I had a problem with Action Scheduler tables. The support helped me very quickly to solve my issue.<br />In less than one day, the support gave me all instructions to follow, and my problem was gone :)<br />Excellent support / reactivity / clarity of responses / kindness</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great solution, excellent support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/paul-filkin/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a5a2c5e8616180a070cafc0516bb3e3e1be26f2fef62a4d6be0d4f677a68b66a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a5a2c5e8616180a070cafc0516bb3e3e1be26f2fef62a4d6be0d4f677a68b66a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/paul-filkin/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Paul Filkin</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 9, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Possibly the best support I’ve had… not just fast but also on a Sunday. Continued through the day and supported me in trying find ways to bend woo commerce with code snippets. Very helpful and I got there before the end of the day. Highly recommend this solution for the product and its flexibility, and the great support.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Outstanding eCommerce Solution!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mochtafeez/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1f53512998aa7a40eef0e7298a9e869d02ebcac219f1e5db4479ff48f5db936b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1f53512998aa7a40eef0e7298a9e869d02ebcac219f1e5db4479ff48f5db936b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mochtafeez/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mochtafeez</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 7, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WooCommerce has completely transformed the way I run my online store. The integration with WordPress is seamless, and the flexibility it offers is unmatched. From customizable product pages to a wide range of plugins and payment gateways, everything just works. The user interface is intuitive, and even as a non-developer, I was able to set up my store with ease. Support from the community and documentation is top-notch. Highly recommended for anyone serious about building a professional online shop!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fast and reliable support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/luniumlondon/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/60054c171fb5d7a357cec1b927f83e0980046c2bb4f530ba3948ea7db3674308?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/60054c171fb5d7a357cec1b927f83e0980046c2bb4f530ba3948ea7db3674308?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/luniumlondon/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">luniumlondon</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 4, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>always a pleasure dealing with the woocommerce support team. They’ve helped me countless of times</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:146:\"Everything you need to launch an online store in days and keep it growing for years. From your first sale to millions in revenue, Woo is with you.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.10.3.5.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=3235205\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:9:\"ecommerce\";s:9:\"ecommerce\";s:12:\"online-store\";s:12:\"online store\";s:11:\"sell-online\";s:11:\"sell online\";s:4:\"shop\";s:4:\"shop\";s:13:\"shopping-cart\";s:13:\"shopping cart\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:522:{s:6:\"10.0.0\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.10.0.0.zip\";s:11:\"10.0.0-rc.1\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.10.0.0-rc.1.zip\";s:11:\"10.0.0-rc.2\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.10.0.0-rc.2.zip\";s:6:\"10.0.1\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.10.0.1.zip\";s:6:\"10.0.2\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.10.0.2.zip\";s:6:\"10.0.3\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.10.0.3.zip\";s:6:\"10.0.4\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.